# quorum lightnode for Python

## install

```bash
pip install -U quorum-lightnode
```

## use quorum-lightnode

### join group and get group seed from local

```bash
export PYTHONPATH=.
python example/join_group.py
```

### send post

```bash
export PYTHONPATH=.
python example/send_post.py
```
